# Testing Requirements

| Layer                 | Tool                      | Minimum Coverage                          |
| --------------------- | ------------------------- | ----------------------------------------- |
| Utilities & libraries | **Jest**                  | ⩾ 90 % lines                              |
| React components      | **React Testing Library** | Render + interaction tests                |
| Pages & flows         | **Cypress**               | Happy-path for every major flow           |

Write tests alongside code: `component.test.tsx`, `lib.spec.ts`.
